channel.title: UK A Level subjects revision [Includes Maths, Physics, Computing and Chemistry]
channel.description:
Breezing around on the internet today, i found a deposit of VERY helpful A level revision guides. Perfect for what you need to study when you revise.
Full document list: http://www.scribd.com/haxan7/documents
Credit to Hassan Nadeem for the uploads, though i don't think he's been active for years...
Have fun :P
